<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id779570b6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s430h–12"><num value="430h–12">§ 430h–12.</num><heading> Administration</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall administer any properties acquired under sections 430h–10 to 430h–13 of this title as part of the Vicksburg National Military Park in accordance with applicable laws and regulations.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id779570b7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/107/238/s4">Pub. L. 107–238, § 4</ref>, <date date="2002-10-11">Oct. 11, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/1486">116 Stat. 1486</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
